items.title: Times Square to feature patriotic ball drop for New Year's Eve
items.description: The New Year's Eve ball drop in New York City will sparkle in red, white, and blue to kick off celebrations for the U.S.'s 250th birthday in 2026

items.title: Hawaii's Big Island bans feeding feral cats in an effort to help endangered native species
items.description: Hawaii's Big Island is banning people from feeding feral cats in an effort to protect native species, including an endangered goose

items.title: Rain-soaked California still at risk of floods and high surf
items.description: A strong storm system that has brought relentless winds, rain and snowfall to California is expected to ease

items.title: Storm system threatens more rainfall Christmas Day over waterlogged Southern California
items.description: Rain from a powerful winter storm that swept across Southern California has begun to taper off

items.title: California drivers warned to reconsider Christmas travel plans ahead of storms
items.description: California officials are urging holiday travelers to avoid the roads on Christmas Eve and Christmas Day
